[
  {
    "filename": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_947.pdf",
    "page_index": 947,
    "core_content": {
      "parsing_res_list": [
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "纸杯龙：由多个纸杯制作而成。纸杯上打孔，用丝线绳系住。",
          "block_bbox": [
            404,
            432,
            834,
            605
          ],
          "block_id": 0,
          "block_order": 1
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "想一想",
          "block_bbox": [
            139,
            693,
            368,
            772
          ],
          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "如何用简单的材料和插接方法制作一条工艺龙呢?\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            96,
            821,
            802,
            947
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "",
          "block_bbox": [
            942,
            3,
            2186,
            1006
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "龙的制作主要分为体和头两部分。先明确艺龙的结构特点是由多个圆柱体连接成。根据这特点，我们可选取纸杯、胡萝段、秸秆段、纸筒等材料，巧妙连接成长弯曲的龙体，表现龙腾飞的动感。龙头部较复杂，要根据造型特点和材料特点研究做法，表现龙的威猛。做好后还要加龙尾、鳍、角爪等，并加以装饰，使龙显得神采奕奕。",
          "block_bbox": [
            96,
            1052,
            1997,
            1347
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "练一练",
          "block_bbox": [
            141,
            1410,
            366,
            1490
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "纸杯龙：由多个纸杯制作而成。在纸杯口和纸杯底上剪切口，然后根据龙的动态进行插合。龙头由两个纸杯制作，龙须就是杯口的边，眼睛是两个杯底。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            93,
            2703,
            709,
            2935
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "请世\n\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            1231,
            1419,
            2156,
            2178
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "尝试用自己喜欢的材料进行插接练习。",
          "block_bbox": [
            182,
            1560,
            951,
            1618
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "国\n\nA1\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            0,
            1681,
            1226,
            2606
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "ii ",
          "block_bbox": [
            754,
            2465,
            1426,
            3046
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "小提示\n\n纸杯插接的剪切口要与杯口\n的弧形相同。\n\n",
